h3. Ingrediants

* 2x Garlic Cloves
* 500g diced Beef/chicken
* 5x shallots
* Mushrooms
* Chicken/beef stock
* tblsp tomato paste
* paprika
* 1/4 cup of wine/sherry (optional)
200ml cream

h3. Method

# Crush garlic and fry with meat until meat is brown 
# Remove meat from pan and leave to side
# Put shallots, mushrooms and stock in a pan and cook until simmering, then add tomato paste and paprika
# Simmer for about 10mins, then add meat
# Simmer for a further 10mins with lid off, then add wine
# Simmer for a while, then just before serving, stir through cream
# Serve on rice
